## Traps

- Edit tool loses Read-tracking across many-file Reads: `Read(limit=N)`
  followed by Edit sometimes errors "File has not been read yet".
  Workaround: full Read without `limit` before each Edit, or smaller
  Edit batches.
- `git pull` on main produced stuck mid-merge state after this session's
  multi-PR merges. Fix: `git reset --hard origin/main` (preserve
  untracked first); `git merge --abort` alone did not clear the index.
- BLAKE2b in `kailash.utils.url_credentials.fingerprint_secret` trips
  `py/weak-sensitive-data-hashing` on CodeQL — alert #10861 DISMISSED
  as documented false-positive. New BLAKE2b on credential-named vars
  will re-trip.
- Python 3.11/3.12 + pydantic-core SecretStr: construction-based tests
  of `AzureEntra(api_key=...)` crash with `SystemError: error return
  without exception set`. Use structural grep tests for migration
